code: public static EvictionType getEvictionType(String name) {     if (name == null) {         return null.     }     for (EvictionType evictionType : values) {         if (evictionType.toString().equalsIgnoreCase(name) || evictionType.name().equalsIgnoreCase(name)) {             return evictionType.         }     }     throw new IllegalArgumentException(String.format("Eviction type '%s' is not supported by this component.", name)). }
